\# Release Lines



\## Active Branches



| Release Line | Branch | Status | Notes |

|---|---|---|---|

| Current Development | `main` | Active | New features merge here |

| Release 1.4 | `release/1.4` | Active | Hotfixes allowed |

| Release 1.3 | `release/1.3` | Maintenance | Critical fixes only |



\## Release Rules



\- New features are not allowed directly on release branches.

\- Hotfixes must target the affected release branch.

\- Fixes made on release branches must be merged back to `main`.

\- Maintenance release branches only accept critical fixes.



\## Freeze Window



\- During freeze, only approved hotfixes can merge into release branches.

\- Feature merges to `main` can continue unless release manager blocks them.



